text: Joel Bruce King (born 30 October 2000) is an Australian professional soccer player. He plays for Sydney FC in the A-League Men and for the Australia men's national soccer team (nicknamed the "Socceroos"). ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Australian men's soccer players Category:People from Wollongong Category:Sportspeople from New South Wales Category:2022 FIFA World Cup players
